casebody.data:
October 18, 1949.

Rehearing Denied.

No. 101. No. 102. Garsson v. United States; and Garsson v. United States,

338 U. S. 830. Motions for extension of time to file petitions for rehearing denied.

The Chief Justice, Mr. Justice Clark, and Mr. Justice Minton took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.
